  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective randomized Study comparing Weight loss, Esophageal Motility and Reflux
      in lap. Gastric Bypass vs. lap. Banded-Gastric Bypass using the A.M.I. Soft Gastric Bypass
      Band (B-Band.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
